posting_body: ['PROPERTY INFO', 'ID: 302778166', 'Rent: $2,400 / Month', 'Beds: 1', 'Bath: 1', 'Available Date: 08/01/2022', 'Broker Fee: One Month', 'Pet: Cats and Small Dogs Negotiable', 'Rent Includes:: Heat, Hot Water and one parking space', 'Parking:: 1 off-street parking is included', 'Spacious one bedroom in an unbelievable Brookline location, steps away from the D train, Longwood Medical and close to Brookline Village, Washington Square and Coolidge Corner-available 8/1!', 'This beautiful unit features newly finished hardwood floors, fresh paint throughout, a nicely updated kitchen and bath, TONS of closet space and LAUNDRY IN THE UNIT!', 'Monthly rent includes heat, hot water AND ONE OFF STREET PARKING SPACE.', 'Small dogs and cats will be considered.', 'For further information and showings call Heidi at 617-699-4568!', 'FEATURES', 'Dishwasher', 'Hardwood Floors', 'High Ceiling', 'Laundry in Unit', 'Modern Bath', 'Modern Kitchen', 'Oven/Range', 'Refrigerator', 'Separate Kitchen', 'Walk-In Closet', 'Heidi Shenker', 'Heidi Shenker Real Estate', '617-699-4568', 'The information in this listing may have been gathered from third party sources including the owner and public records.', 'Listings are subject to errors and omissions.', 'Heidi Shenker Real Estate disclaims any and all representations or warranties as to the accuracy of this information.', 'Heidi Shenker Real Estate is an Equal Housing Opportunity Agency.', 'Photos may not always be of the actual apartment, at times sample images are used to make a general representation.']
